judgment_text:
hvn IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY ORDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION SUIT NO. 1539 OF 1979 Renuka Anantrai Vora and Ors.

Plaintiffs Versus Kirtikumar Fulchadn Vora and anr.

Defendants Mr. A. Shinde i/by Halai & Co. for plaintiff No. 1. Ms. Kavita Shah i/by Mr. A.G.Shah for respondent. CORAM : R.D. DHANUKA,J. DATED : SEPTEMBER 03, 2013 P.C. By an order dated 31st July, 2013 this court directed the Prothonotary to call for records and proceedings of Suit No. 1539 of 1979 from City Civil Court Bombay to this court to ascertain whether suit can be tried in this court. If such direction has not been complied with so far shall be complied with within two weeks from today. (R.D. DHANUKA,J.)
